OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,FCutting red tape, adopting digital
OL,7,Fcurrencies, and protecting its
OL,8,Ffinancial status are just some of the
OL,9,Fways Jersey hopes to attract new
OL,10,Fbusiness to the island.
OL,12,FIt comes as a new government report
OL,13,Fwarns that without change, the
OL,14,Fisland's market share in the global
OL,15,Fsector will be eroded.
OL,17,FThe 'Time to Win' plan is the first in-
OL,18,Fdepth strategic review of Jersey's
OL,19,Ffinancial sector since 2014, and hopes
OL,20,Fto future-proof the industry through
OL,21,Fmodernisation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,FCurrently, Jersey's financial sector
OL,7,Fis worth more than #4 billion,
OL,8,Fproviding #6 in every #10 of tax
OL,9,Frevenue received.
OL,11,FHowever, there are concerns that the
OL,12,Fisland is lagging behind other
OL,13,Fjurisdictions, particularly in Asia
OL,14,Fand the Middle East.
OL,16,FSir Howard Davies, the former NatWest
OL,17,Fchairman who led the independent panel
OL,18,Fof experts to create the 'Time to Win'
OL,19,Fstrategy, says the island needs to be
OL,20,Fmore attractive to business.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,F"Things have got to change", Sir
OL,7,FDavies told ITV News. "It's not a
OL,8,Fcatastrophe, but it does mean that
OL,9,Fyou've got to run faster to stand
OL,10,Fstill than you did in the past."
OL,12,FThe strategy hopes to sell Jersey as a
OL,13,FBritish-oriented financial centre with
OL,14,Fstrong connectivity to London, coupled
OL,15,Fwith an established base of
OL,16,Fknowledgeable people in the world of
OL,17,Ffinance.
OL,19,FThe main action points include:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,FDeputy Elaine Millar, the island's
OL,7,FTreasury Minister, told ITV News: "We
OL,8,Freally need to recognise that there's
OL,9,Fno room for complacency in Jersey.
OL,11,F"We've thought for a long time that
OL,12,Fpeople are lucky to come here, but
OL,13,Fit's now the other way around.
OL,15,F"(We) really just need to go for
OL,16,Fgrowth, so really making sure that we
OL,17,Fare welcoming to business and that we
OL,18,Freally want to go out and grab it."
OL,26,@wD@BpmwD@Epn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,FDeputy Ian Gorst, Minister for
OL,7,FExternal Relations and Financial
OL,8,FServices, believes that while Jersey
OL,9,Fis "already winning business", a new
OL,10,Fframework is needed to compete with
OL,11,Fother jurisdictions.
OL,13,F"Whilst we've had those decades of
OL,14,Fsuccess, some competitors have only
OL,15,Fbeen around for 20 years, and they are
OL,16,Fmuch more digitally enabled, they are
OL,17,Fmuch more responsive, so for us, it's
OL,18,Fabout the factors around our offering.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,F"Some international clients want some
OL,7,Fof their business structured through
OL,8,Fthe Middle East or the Far East, but
OL,9,Fthey also want some of their European
OL,10,For maybe American businesses
OL,11,Fstructured through part of the British
OL,12,Ffamily.
OL,14,F"That's the business we're trying to
OL,15,Fwin."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,FHowever, while plenty of changes are
OL,7,Fnoted, such as streamlining regulatory
OL,8,Fsystems and making it easier for
OL,9,Ftalented people to come to the island,
OL,10,Fthe report also highlights the
OL,11,Fimportance of keeping what makes
OL,12,FJersey an attractive place for
OL,13,Fbusiness in the first place.
OL,15,FJill Britton, the Director General at
OL,16,Fthe Jersey Financial Services
OL,17,FCommission, says, "In some places of
OL,18,Four framework, it is complex, so this
OL,19,Fis a great opportunity to simplify.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,F"Over the years, international
OL,7,Fstandards have increased. There's a
OL,8,Fhigher expectation, and it's more
OL,9,Fcomplex. I think it would be wrong for
OL,10,Fus not to take a step back and see how
OL,11,Fwe can simplify and make things less
OL,12,Fcomplex.
OL,14,F"However, we absolutely still need to
OL,15,Ffit into what is true to us, which is
OL,16,Faround high standards of compliance
OL,17,Fwith the international expectations
OL,18,Fthat are set on us.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,F"We have the foundations in place, our
OL,7,Ftax position, the regulations, the
OL,8,Fquality of financial resources, and
OL,9,Fthe name and brands that we have are
OL,10,Fabsolutely internationally recognised
OL,11,F- and that all makes Jersey really,
OL,12,Freally attractive."
OL,14,FOne of the key changes the report
OL,15,Fhighlights is making Jersey receptive
OL,16,Fto new technologies, particularly
OL,17,Fcryptocurrency.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,FDescribed as "one of the potential
OL,7,Fleaders for growth" by the Treasury
OL,8,FMinister, the report wants to create
OL,9,Fan ecosystem where financial
OL,10,Finstitutions feel comfortable
OL,11,Finvesting and exchanging
OL,12,Fcryptocurrency.
OL,14,F"There are lots of younger people now
OL,15,F- younger wealth creators - who are
OL,16,Fholding money in cryptocurrencies,"
OL,17,FDeputy Millar explained.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,F"We need to recognise that and make
OL,7,Fsure that we are open to regulating
OL,8,Fand allowing businesses that focus on
OL,9,Fdigital currencies, and that we do
OL,10,Ffind a way of allowing them into the
OL,11,Fisland."
OL,13,FAlex Dunsdon, a cryptocurrency
OL,14,Finvestor, says Jersey needs to be
OL,15,Fprepared for what he believes will be
OL,16,F"a systemic change" in how business is
OL,17,Fconducted.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,F"You've got an industry that's grown
OL,7,Fup on a certain set of rails with a
OL,8,Fcertain way of doing things that has
OL,9,Fworked very well for the past 40 to 60
OL,10,Fyears," Alex explained.
OL,12,F"But you used to go to Blockbuster for
OL,13,Fvideo, and that was when we all had
OL,14,FVHSs. Then, suddenly, streaming came
OL,15,Falong, and that is an extra
OL,16,Fexistential level event because the
OL,17,Fwhole platform that you're built on
OL,18,Fhas changed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,F"That is what's happening with AI and
OL,7,Fcrypto, and it's not just a little
OL,8,Fchange of product here and a little
OL,9,Finnovation there. It's a fundamentally
OL,10,Fnew platform that is quicker, faster,
OL,11,Fcheaper, and better, and it's going to
OL,12,Fget mass adoption really, really
OL,13,Fquickly."
OL,15,FFor islanders, there is concern over
OL,16,Fhow bringing in more banks could see
OL,17,Fnew infrastructure, funneling money
OL,18,Faway from the issues directly
OL,19,Faffecting them.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,FHowever, the Treasury Minister
OL,7,Fbelieves that residents will
OL,8,Fultimately benefit from the proposed
OL,9,Fchanges.
OL,11,FPart of the report suggests that
OL,12,FJersey's schools, housing, and
OL,13,Fentertainment offerings all need to be
OL,14,Faddressed.
OL,16,F"It won't mean making more buildings,
OL,17,Fbecause we have to recognise that
OL,18,Fdigitalisation will, in some cases,
OL,19,Freduce employment," Deputy Millar
OL,20,Fsaid, "but it means people can work
OL,21,Fmore effectively and more productively.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1773774690
OL,3,CWhy Jersey is being urged to invest in
OL,4,Cdigital currency to remain competitive
OL,6,F"It will also generate more revenue
OL,7,Ffor the government. The Financial
OL,8,FServices already producers 60% of our
OL,9,Fincome as government, and that's what
OL,10,Ffunds health, education, and a large
OL,11,Fpart of social security.
OL,13,F"The government can then use that
OL,14,Fmoney to make sure we are providing
OL,15,Feffective services for the population."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
